{"tid":538464,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"應該點樣追一個大我四年嘅女仔？","createTime":"2018-01-23T15:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T10:09:59.000Z","uid":147978,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2cee650a5ce5b1e5ee5f7cc7f4538122cd01bfe4","tid":538464,"uid":147978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T15:40:42.000Z","msg":"小弟今年year1 <br />\n因為做part time識左個大我四年嘅姐姐 <br />\n佢就喺嗰度做full time<br />\n我地工作上溝通唔多 但一有時間就會傾計 有時仲有少少曖味 <br />\n雖然我地唔算好熟 但都feel到佢有時想透過啲行為親近啲<br />\n而我都對佢好心動<br />\n但諗極都諗唔到一個好啲嘅方法可以冇咁狗公得來又可以追到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇吓各位巴絲有冇咩好辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPs. 佢係一個幾單純嘅女仔 啱啱大專畢業 而小弟就大學一年級"},{"pid":"ec741e22ccf115ab9d2be074efb68c0e3fdcc322","tid":538464,"uid":137436,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T15:54:21.000Z","msg":"唔好成日發癲啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> A0死毒撚 日撚日係到ff識到女朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底你真人係咪唔會出街 ？ 隱青果堆？"},{"pid":"21be03d419871f910c76766cb8da439d705c39f3","tid":538464,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T15:56:53.000Z","msg":"既然曖昧咪順期自然 唔存在追唔追既問題喎清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非你ff姐"},{"pid":"3b4583eebdaa967ef131ad51f755c6ce07e93da1","tid":538464,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T15:57:30.000Z","msg":"無圖點幫你"},{"pid":"ceb05f55ea638458ea5a7aca7bd7213046664663","tid":538464,"uid":143192,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:32:54.000Z","msg":"拎住束花同佢講:受唔受溝呀"},{"pid":"f40a021cfb18d992ba810899c8ace9e47fb696fa","tid":538464,"uid":70496,"like